data.description: Absolutely Gorgeous Home on 9.08 Acres IN CITY LIMITS! Custom built, Move In ready, 4 bed, 3 bath home tucked back in your own private wooded oasis. There is so much room for all your needs with 16' ceilings, an updated kitchen with granite countertops, an inviting sunroom, a formal living room/formal dining, extra space for office, pond and gardening spots, and front deck that makes you feel like you are in the treetops. This home is a must-see. House is on City Water. Plenty of storage for your toys and hobbies with multiple storage buildings onsite! Extra Water source outside- Well Water for Gardening and yard play.  Don't miss out on seeing this unique home! Seller will entertain offers!
